\par\plain {The ancient sentinel of the Illusory Forest loomed over the shattered laboratory, its obsidian-black scales gleaming under the fractured moonlight. Its six pairs of glowing red eyes, locked onto Catherine with an almost calculating gaze.}
\par\plain {The beast let out a slow, reverberating growl.}
\par\plain {A blur of black scales and outstretched talons shot toward Catherine with terrifying speed. She pivoted on her heel, barely dodging as the beast\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s claws }{\f0\fs24\b0 raked}{ across the stone where she had stood moments before, carving deep gashes into the earth.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Catherine retaliated.}{\f0\fs24\b1  }{She hurled a jagged slab of stone toward the dragon, transmuting it mid-air into a hail of sharp-edged weapons\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 spears of iron, serrated daggers, bolts of steel. They }{\f0\fs24\b1 shot forward}{ like an arrow storm, striking the dragon\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s gleaming black scales.}
